title: God’s Got Your Back Part 2
description:
Don’t get stuck rehearsing the wrong story.

In “God’s Got Your Back Part 2,” Pastor Steven Furtick reminds us to let God lead by faith instead of being driven by our fear.

If you’ve just made a decision for Christ, please respond HERE: http://ele.vc/tIepfr

To support this ministry and help us continue to reach people all around the world click here: http://www.elevationchurch.org/giving/

Scripture References:

Isaiah 30, verse 21

1 Kings 19, verses 1-18
